thread.title: Cinderrella

author: Cinderrella
title: Cinderrella
text: Prior to installation there was no LTE connectivity within the residence and only spotty connectivity outside. With installation, even though I was not able to attain 20 feet vertical and 50 feel linear separation between the outdoor and indoor antennas, there are still four green bars on the power supply to the indoor antenna; I typically see 103 dBls of signal strength, sufficient enough for voice, text and internet connectivity. A good investment and I have bragged of my appreciation of the connectivity to friends who can now connect with me with assurance.
